        "TileImage": "$($repository 4600e742-9c2a-402b-a84b-90f7a408eb74).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning 47!\r\rYour next target is the current mayor of a small italian city who was recently blackmailed by his party&apos;s political opposition. If he doesn&apos;t sabotage the campaign of his own party, everyone in the city will know of all of his perversions. Something involving diapers, just to name one. Either way, the mayor&apos;s party has hired us to take him out, and also his confidant bodyguard who could also broker the deal with the opposition, even after the mayor&apos;s death..",
